    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, distinguished by eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement with VAC-coated shells and ARP hardware, ensuring long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, and the Electronic Damping Control (EDC) system provides factory-spec rebound and compression. The paint maintains its original luster with no orange peel or rock chips, while the interior Novillo leather remains supple. This is an uncompromising, turn-key machine for the discerning purist.",
