      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish with no rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further preserved by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is in absolute pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without any creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Every feature, including the advanced driver-assistance systems and the premium infotainment suite, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is perfect, supported by a comprehensive, top-tier service history and a clean title. This is a rare, investment-quality example for a buyer who demands perfection. I welcome any third-party inspection to verify its exceptional state.",
